text: Jo Darr Gya Woh Marr Gya () is a Pakistani Urdu movie which starred Neeli, Javed Sheikh, Atiqa Odho, Reema and Nadeem. The movie was released in the summer of 1995 and earned major revenue for its production studio. It was directed by Iqbal Kashmiri and was produced by Evernew Studios. The English title is Scared.
